{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3f065de2e9","title":"转发张体学关于湖北分粮到户等情况汇报的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"23cbc96702","index":0,"year":1959,"month":6,"day":20,"articleId":"3f065de2e9"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji42","name":"毛泽东全集第42卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/42-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji42":{"comments":[{"id":"938acc98cd","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"3f065de2e9","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"张体学，当时任湖北省省长。"},{"id":"1f73f7e1a9","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"3f065de2e9","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指张体学1959年6月16日晨关于小麦入库、分粮到户及抓手工业等情况的电话汇报。张体学说，湖北的小麦已快打完了，入库进展不算很快，正在抓。粮食以人分等定量到户后，情况大变，小队干部和农民欢天喜地，天队和公社干部仍有些不通。现在省委决定直接与群众见面了。可以办得通。渔民已经归队不少，湖里开始有人捕鱼了。抓了一下手工业之后，产品有所增加。同日，国务院副总理兼财政部部长季先念将这一电话内容转报周恩来。毛泽东的批语就写在李先念的报告上。"},{"id":"707aa9ae62","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"3f065de2e9","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"尚昆，即杨尚昆，当时任中共中央书记处候补书记、中央办公厅主任。"}],"contents":[{"id":"f2a4782133","type":"title","text":"转发张体学关于湖北分粮到户等情况汇报的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"3f065de2e9"},{"id":"938acc98cd","type":"paragraph","text":"此件回请尚昆可用电报发各省、市、区党委研究。粮食要分到户。另要大抓副食品、日用工业品，恢复手工业","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"3f065de2e9"},{"id":"1f73f7e1a9","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"3f065de2e9"},{"id":"707aa9ae62","type":"paragraph","text":"六月二十日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"3f065de2e9"}],"page":{"id":"d935a531e7","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"3f065de2e9","start":88,"end":88}}}},"__N_SSG"